      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it. I've made sure to keep up with everything so it's ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something reliable and well-loved that won't break the bank, this is the one! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 28900.0,
