      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This example boasts sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a predictable chassis balance thanks to a healthy limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, and the braking system provides firm pedal feedback. While the aesthetic shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A purist\u2019s specification for those who prioritize mechanical excellence and driving dynamics.",
